Hello,

The App=C2=A0Review Guidelines have been revised to support updated policie=
s and to provide clarification. Please review the changes below:
https://c.apple.com/r?v=3D2&a=3Do2CKfLM8dAL7lynfnyn7UJR94mniF31x6BQ8mUoKnZV=
GdhMPez2mA%2FDwb9NtLPnk7QBa5O5wm2K0lwSzzbxwCsMQMkpHcil36SzSYuqO2hfxEMFGsJN3=
Bc5n6lcGfrVKME4ygiePZyqKMPv%2BEcnZ0ydGvdOE7XgI%2Bqx5W3i3HzF6fFRP%2F46EH6h80=
D0whi%2BPsfDx1EbPiEkvVnTx0LkqSTj1Xc84qwj8R0Me8C9%2BFRFV1pO%2BT1oD8dpm0833ND=
z0gMCMz26sbri6DNlIJbHSGg%3D%3D

=E2=80=A2          1.2.1(a): This new guideline specifies that creator apps=
 must provide a way for users to identify content that exceeds the app=E2=
=80=99s age rating, and use an age restriction mechanism based on verified =
or declared age to limit access by underage users.    =20

=E2=80=A2          2.5.10: This language has been deleted ("Apps should not=
 be submitted with empty ad banners or test advertisements.=E2=80=9D).    =
=20

=E2=80=A2          3.2.2(ix): Clarified that loan apps may not charge a max=
imum APR higher than 36%, including costs and fees, and may not require rep=
ayment in full in 60 days or less.    =20

=E2=80=A2      4.1(c): This new guideline specifies that you cannot use ano=
ther developer's icon, brand, or product name in your app's icon or name, w=
ithout approval from the developer.         =20

=E2=80=A2      4.7: Clarifies that HTML5 and JavaScript mini apps and mini =
games are in scope of the guideline.     =20

=E2=80=A2      4.7.2: Clarifies that apps offering software not embedded in=
 the binary may not extend or expose native platform APIs or technologies t=
o the software without prior permission from Apple.     =20

=E2=80=A2      4.7.5: Clarifies that apps offering software not embedded in=
 the binary must provide a way for users to identify content that exceeds t=
he app=E2=80=99s age rating, and use an age restriction mechanism based on =
verified or declared age to limit access by underage users.   =20

=E2=80=A2      5.1.1(ix): Adds crypto exchanges to the list of apps that pr=
ovide services in highly regulated fields.     =20

=E2=80=A2 5.1.2(i): Clarifies that you must clearly disclose where personal=
 data will be shared with third parties, including with third-party AI, and=
 obtain explicit permission before doing so.



If you have any questions, contact=C2=A0us.=20
https://developer.apple.com/contact/topic/select

The Apple Developer Relations Team=20

